<text><body><cb:div>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0246a" xml:id="I01.0092.0246a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0246a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 92</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0246a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>道略等造神碑像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0247a" xml:id="I01.0092.0247a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0247a01"/><p xml:id="pI01p0247a0101" cb:type="pre">自夢影東翻。金人感帝。像法肇興。鳩摩啟悟。方知城芥
<lb ed="I" n="0247a02"/>易窮。五衣時往。雲電屢馳。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">石</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">光</unclear>何速。若夫智出非<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">恒</unclear>。道
<lb ed="I" n="0247a03"/>光大地。德被天中。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">威</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">羅</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">世</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">界</unclear>。莫不發迹紫宮。□軀兜率。
<lb ed="I" n="0247a04"/>越度生死之河。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">飛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">憑</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沸</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">流</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>海。而四生夥雜。八<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">徑</unclear>紛綸。
<lb ed="I" n="0247a05"/>壽等芭蕉。業同泡<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">沬</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">然</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">鑒</unclear>降澤。顯跡迦夷。應權雙樹。
<lb ed="I" n="0247a06"/>見從忍土。布慈雲<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">於</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">無</unclear>邊。注法雨於六道。懸明鏡於重
<lb ed="I" n="0247a07"/>惛。炳金燈於萇夜。然則神珠照灼。暎寶塔於空中。甘露
<lb ed="I" n="0247a08"/>禎祥。潤枯萌於世上。若乃久墮慾海。不識沈厄之苦。長
<lb ed="I" n="0247a09"/>處火山。詎愁燌燎之痛矣。是以邑師比丘僧道略。體白
<lb ed="I" n="0247a10"/>六道。獨懷二覺。雄才勇志。摠判三乘。澄華皎淨。與琉璃
<lb ed="I" n="0247a11"/>合潔。素質鏗鏘。與<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">隨</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">珠</unclear>角曜。故知二鼠之暴不停。四<note n="0247001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">虵＝蛇【史】</note><note n="0247001" resp="ihp" type="mod">虵【佛拓】，蛇【史】</note><app n="0247001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">蛇</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">虵</rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0247a12"/>之毒萇在。遂能共邑義三百餘人等。託志菩提。建崇弘
<lb ed="I" n="0247a13"/>願。石出藍田。求工班爾。敬造神碑一所。尊像八堪。龍螭
<lb ed="I" n="0247a14"/>鉅鏤。若雲山之烈。彩麗拔妙。形似七寶之莊嚴。而改天
<lb ed="I" n="0247a15"/>動地之奇。窮神盡聖之巧。閻浮娑婆之珍。眾生大慈之
<lb ed="I" n="0247a16"/>業。然則地兼爽塏。比竹林而並麗。寺帶良田。匹鹿菀而
<lb ed="I" n="0247a17"/>不殊。花果<note n="0247002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣱦＝氛【史】</note><note n="0247002" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣱦【佛拓】，氛【史】</note><app n="0247002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">氛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𣱦</rdg></app>氳。桂蘭綺合。靈芝勺藥。布護階廷。房廡周
<lb ed="I" n="0247a18"/>通。斜□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">繡</unclear>出。掎捔璧璫。浮樑止雪。蓮錢遶淥井。碧水類
<lb ed="I" n="0247a19"/>清泉。□樓交葛。甍鐸參差。羽翮翳林。<note n="0247003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">飡＝餐【史】</note><note n="0247003" resp="ihp" type="mod">飡【佛拓】，餐【史】</note><app n="0247003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">餐</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">飡</rdg></app>聽妙響。鴛鸞雙
<lb ed="I" n="0247a20"/>樹。翫好真音。至於青風朗扇。鍾聲相和。莫覺擅指。合掌
<lb ed="I" n="0247a21"/>南<note n="0247a2101" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【佛拓】【史】</note><app n="0247a2101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】【史】">旡</rdg></app>。遊歷四禪之境。觀入三脫之中。內安万練之僧。招
<lb ed="I" n="0247a22"/>精進之士。銀爐鼓炎。百和騰烟。錫響讚聲。定崩煩<note n="0247004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31104"/>＝惱【史】</note><note n="0247004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31104"/>【佛拓】，惱【史】</note><app n="0247004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">惱</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31104"/></rdg></app>。有
<lb ed="I" n="0247a23"/>性厥靈。永登寶地。凡命含品。普昇淨土。籍斯功德。遍沾
<lb ed="I" n="0247a24"/>玄劫。芳謠時歇。銘歌何窮。其詞曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0247a25"/>元沖眇邈。正教終歸。三明自達。六識雲飛。浮虛兜極。颺
<lb ed="I" n="0247a26"/>影紫微。懸空遊息。三界徘徊。地居勝土。寺遶花蓮。周迴
<lb ed="I" n="0247a27"/>風觀。遍帶流淵。上干浮漢。下際幽泉。方須玉櫂。事籍金<note n="0247005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">舩＝船【史】</note><note n="0247005" resp="ihp" type="mod">舩【佛拓】，船【史】</note><app n="0247005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">船</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">舩</rdg></app>。
<lb ed="I" n="0247a28"/>踵茲洪福。為<note n="0247006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣴴＝海【史】</note><note n="0247006" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣴴【佛拓】，海【史】</note><app n="0247006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">海</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">𣴴</rdg></app>舟樑。發心何遠。彼岸猶長。天人覺<note n="0247007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB31105"/>＝悟【史】</note><note n="0247007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB31105"/>【佛拓】，悟【史】</note><app n="0247007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">悟</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB31105"/></rdg></app>。超
<lb ed="I" n="0247a29"/>投太康。所願閻浮。同登淨鄉。大齊武平二年歲次辛卯九月十五日建</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>
